245
00:13:22,632 --> 00:13:25,131
Nampaknya mereka ingin mendapatkan maklumat

246
00:13:25,132 --> 00:13:26,831
daripada Detektif Mouri dan kamu.

247
00:13:26,832 --> 00:13:29,331
Adakah mereka anggota Organisasi Hitam?

